tickets.description: NBA Preseason - Milwaukee Bucks at Miami Heat

injuries.longComment: Sears did not suit up during Summer League due to a left calf strain. The Alabama product latched on with the Bucks on a two-way contract after going undrafted in the 2025 NBA Draft.
injuries.shortComment: Sears (calf) did not play in Friday's 93-92 Summer League loss to the Heat.

injuries.longComment: Bouyea scored 20 points in Saturday's loss to the Cavaliers but was held out of Sunday's back-to-back matchup against the Clippers for rest and didn't appear in another game the rest of Summer League. He logged five regular-season appearances (one start) for the Bucks in 2024-25, averaging 3.4 points, 2.0 assists and 1.0 rebound in 12.4 minutes per contest.
